items.title: Fanvibe
items.description:
Check-in to games to chat and trash-talk with friends who are also watching. Get scores and breaking news sent straight to your iPhone. Fanvibe covers the NBA, NFL, MLB, NHL, college basketball, college football, and the English Premier League.

Fanvibe Features Include:

-Your Sports Pulse: A custom feed with news, scores and your friendsâ€™ activity.

-Game Check-Ins: Tell your friends what youâ€™re watching and see what games your friends are watching. Never ask, â€œDid you see that game?â€ again!

-Personalized Scoreboard: Real-time scores, live game details, alerts and score updates.

-Favorites: Get news and scores for your favorite teams sent straight to your iPhone or iPod touch.

-Friend Finder: Find your friends easily by searching Facebook, Twitter and your address book.

Coming soon: March Madness brackets and World Cup coverage, Cricket, Golf and Tennis.

About Fanvibe

Fanvibe for the iPhone / iPod Touch is the first product from We The Fan, a company dedicated to building new sports products built by and for the sports fan.

items.title: Bountii
items.description:
Bountii is a price search startup that has built a search engine capable of finding shoppers lower and more accurate prices than any existing price comparison service. Currently supplying consumers with pricing information on electronics and appliances, Bountii aims to expand its service to make buying any product online at the best price an effortless experience.

Bountii was founded in the Summer of 2007 by Samir Meghani and John Puskarich. Initial investment was provided by Y Combinator, a venture firm that specializes in funding early stage startups.

items.title: Call9
items.description:
Call9 delivers true Emergency Medicine and Palliative Care at patients'​ bedsides. Currently in Skilled Nursing Facilities, Call9 decreases the time patients wait to see an EM Physician from an average of 64 minutes to moments in emergency situations.

In tandem with 24/7 onsite Clinical Care Specialists*, offsite Emergency Medicine Physicians see, diagnose and treat patients at the bedside via the Call9 proprietary platform. Our focus goes beyond the medicine to assure premium patient-centered care by including patients, caregivers, and families in communications from the start.

Today, our proprietary technology-enabled services reduce cost and increase quality-of-care within elder-care facilities. Tomorrow, we redefine emergency medicine.

*Clinical Care Specialists(TM) are elite emergency responders. Excellent bedside manner and rigorous continuing emergency training make Call9, PC's CCSs a unique specialty.
